'''科伦坡區'''是[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]][[西部省_(斯里蘭卡)|西部省]]的一個區。面積642平方公里。2001年人口2,251,574人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statistics.gov.lk/PopHouSat/PDF/Population/p9p2%20Population%20by%20district%20,%20sex,%20sex%20ratio%20and%20population%20density.pdf |title=2001年人口普查 |accessdate=2008-05-08 |archive-date=2012-05-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67j70arpb?url=http://www.statistics.gov.lk/PopHouSat/PDF/Population/p9p2%20Population%20by%20district%20%2C%20sex%2C%20sex%20ratio%20and%20population%20density.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首府和最大城市為[[科伦坡|科伦坡]]。行政首都[[斯里賈亞瓦德納普拉科特|科特]]也位於本區。

